    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists just try to fix things, but you can't fix something that isn't there anymore. the person i was is gone. there's nothing left to reconnect to. it's like watching a movie of someone else's life and just waiting for the credits to roll. it just feels like a waste of space at this point.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
